\pard\sa280\sl360\slmult1\b\fs28 What if\'85?\par

\pard\sa240\sl360\slmult1\b0\fs24 So, let\rquote s imagine an institution like the State Archives of Belgium, with million of data collected for years, wishes to make them more visible and shareable by publishing them in the LOD cloud. \par
However, as seen in the previous slide, some properties are currently missing to express some concepts.\par
There would be 2 main options for improvement in this case:\par

